Yo this is fire and I’m about to make this into a t-shirt. Who would buy a shirt with this design cause I would I look hot af 😅😅 leave a comment if I get a certain amount of “yes” I will make these shirts asap!

Alot has happened this year in 2022 that I never thought would be possible. Started the year with having covid, ended up being aired on TV, released my debut EP “Insanity” and other songs, put out two music videos, hit over 10k subscribers on Youtube, traveled to different places with @beardoscuriosities and tons of other things that I cant think of right now. Lets see what 2023 brings!

As I reflect on my life and career in general as I am turning the big 3-0 on Friday, I realize that I am doing the damn thing. I do not have management, signed to any record labels, etc. (Although it would be super helpful). I’ve been working hard for years and receiving support from you guys which I am super appreciative. It definitely was not an easy journey. If you been with me from the beginning, you know the shit I went through to get to this point. And if you dont know, I’m happy to talk about it. It got me stronger. I am not done. Cheers to another milestone. 🤘🏼📸: @pixeljournalism

Happy Holidays! Enjoy this time with friends and family! Thank you for a great year! ❤️🤘🏼 Let’s see what 2024 brings!

2023 was a lot and fulfulling. 
- I did two tours this year. One with @livingdeadgirlofficial and the second tour with @influencetheband. Love and miss them both! Please check them out!
- Switched schools and finally on a salary before I turned 30. 
- Increased my private music students clientele 
- Opened up an Oddities store @beardoscuriosities with my love
-Got another fur baby. A naked cat named Deacon
-The year my first neice was born 
-Lost about 15 pounds. Working out is now a part of my morning routine. Thank you @frandejm for introducing me to @e2mfitness 
-Met new people and made new friends. Went out more this year with friends.❤️
-Did another tv show (episode coming out in 2024)
And the list goes on and on. Thank you for being a part of this journey. Happy new year 2024!
How is everyone doing today? How are you spending your week? I am going to be doing lots of planning and practicing. 📸: @crios_photography
